data.description: Single-story home with 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, and a 2-car garage. Spacious formal living room with vaulted ceiling and built-in cabinets and shelves. Family room has ceiling fan, tile floor, and sliding glass door to the covered patio. Kitchen with lots of cabinets and counter tops, tile floor, gas stove, and refrigerator included. Primary bedroom has lighted ceiling fan, mirrored closet doors, and is separate from the other bedrooms. Hall has a built-in linen cabinet. 2nd bedroom with lighted ceiling fan. 3rd bedroom has lighted ceiling fan, and a walk-in closet with a door into the garage. 2 car garage has finished interior, a side door to the front patio, recessed lighting, work bench, and epoxy floor. Laundry in garage includes washer and dryer. Patio in front . Spacious covered patio in back yard  with 2 lighted ceiling fans.
